# Project Rules

Web OS like PC desktop

## Tech Stack

- **Framework:** [Next.js](mdc:https:/nextjs.org) v15.2.4
- **UI Library:** [React](mdc:https:/reactjs.org) v19.1.0
- **Styling:** [Tailwind CSS](mdc:https:/tailwindcss.com) v4.1.4
- **Linting:** [ESLint](mdc:https:/eslint.org) v9.24.0
- **Git Hooks:** [Husky](mdc:https:/typicode.github.io/husky) v9.1.7
- **Commit Linting:** [Commitlint](mdc:https:/commitlint.js.org) v19.8.0
- **Containerization:** [Docker](mdc:https:/www.docker.com)
- **Language:** [TypeScript](mdc:https:/www.typescriptlang.org) v5.8.3
- **Package Manager:** [Bun](mdc:https:/bun.sh) v1.x
- **UI Components:** [Radix UI](mdc:https:/www.radix-ui.com) v1.1.7
- **Icons:** [Lucide React](mdc:https:/lucide.dev) v0.488.0

